window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Ethan Montgomery thought he had his life figured out until the moment he and his best friend, Lincoln, met a woman in a wedding dress drinking wine out of a paper bag. Love has never been in the cards for him because he doesn’t realize what is right in front of him.</p> <p>Lincoln's done his best to ignore his feelings for Ethan and focus on his art. Yet the moment Holland enters the picture, all bets are off and sparks fly.</p> <p>Only Holland is fresh out of a disastrous relationship that ended with her running away from her cheating groom. She’s not sure she can trust a man again—let alone two.</p> <p>But the attraction between them cannot be denied and sometimes there’s no going back—even when their pasts try to break them apart.</p> <p>**Sated in Ink is a friends to lovers, runaway bride, MMF, friends with benefits romance in the Montgomery Ink: Boulder series featuring Ethan, Holland, and Lincoln. Each book can be listened to as a complete standalone. An HEA is guaranteed!**</p>"; 
